  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Patients suspected of adenomatous polyposis were included. The criteria used were more than&#xD;
      10 polyps observed under colonoscopy, and pathological confirmation of adenoma. Clinical data&#xD;
      and pedigree information were collected. The variants of 139 genes associated with different&#xD;
      hereditary cancers and polyposis were screened by NGS, which was performed by Genetron Health&#xD;
      on the HiSeqX-ten sequencing platform.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
